Step-by-Step Setup Instructions
1. Install Python
Download and install Python from the official website: https://www.python.org/downloads/.

During installation, ensure to check the box "Add Python to PATH" so Python can be accessed from the command prompt.

2. Install Required Libraries
After installing Python:

Open Command Prompt (or Terminal on macOS/Linux).

Run the following command to install the necessary Python libraries:


pip install pyttsx3 pygame tk


3. Set Up the Script
Create a folder on your computer and place the script file (antivirus game!.py) inside the folder.

Ensure the images (person.png, person2.png, person3.png, and hehe1.png) are also inside the same folder as the script.

4. Running the Script

open the file with python.
 if it does not work, message me.



